      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">4.705-2</ph> Pay administration records.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d233e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d235e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            Payroll sheets, registers, or their equivalent, of salaries and wages paid to individual employees for each payroll period; change slips; and tax withholding statements: Retain 4 years.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d235e15">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            Clock cards or other time and attendance cards: Retain 2 years.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d235e20">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
						            Paid checks, receipts for wages paid in cash, or other evidence of payments for services rendered by employees: Retain 2 years.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
